EncounterPatientGivenNameSearchParameter

Parameter patient.given:string

Searches for Encounters based on the patient's given name(s) eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Encounter?patient.given={givenName}

ResourceEncounter
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesEncounter
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
